    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Responding to Prices: 'Expensive'",
          "arabic": "الرد على الأسعار: «غالي»"
        },
        "text": "After asking the price, you might want to express if you think something is expensive. The word for 'expensive' is غالي for masculine items and غالية for feminine items.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "ده غالي أوي!",
            "english": "This is very expensive! (masc.)",
            "transliteration": "da ghāli ʾawī!"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "دي غالية شوية.",
            "english": "This is a little expensive. (fem.)",
            "transliteration": "di ghālya shwaya."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Responding to Prices: 'Cheap'",
          "arabic": "الرد على الأسعار: «رخيص»"
        },
        "text": "Conversely, if something is affordable, you can say it's 'cheap'. The word is رخيص for masculine and رخيصة for feminine.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "ده رخيص جدًا.",
            "english": "This is very cheap. (masc.)",
            "transliteration": "da rakhīs giddan."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "دي رخيصة خالص.",
            "english": "This is very cheap. (fem.)",
            "transliteration": "di rakhīṣa khāliṣ."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
