        "title": {
          "english": "Paying with Cash: 'Cash'",
          "arabic": "الدفع كاش: «كاش»"
        },
        "text": "When it comes to payment, 'cash' is a widely used term, often directly adopted from English. In Egyptian Arabic, you'd say كاش.",
