    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Paying with Card: 'Card' / 'Visa'",
          "arabic": "الدفع بالفيزا/الكارت: «فيزا» / «كارت»"
        },
        "text": "For card payments, people generally use the English word 'card' (كارت) or 'Visa' (فيزا) to refer to any credit or debit card. You might ask 'في دفع بالفيزا؟' (Fi dafʿ bi-l-visa?) - 'Is there payment by Visa?'",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "في دفع بالفيزا؟",
