          "arabic": "طلب فاتورة: «فاتورة»"
        },
        "text": "After a purchase, you might need a receipt. The word for 'receipt' or 'invoice' is فاتورة. You can ask for one by saying 'ممكن فاتورة لو سمحت؟' (Momken fatoora law samaḥt?) - 'A receipt please?'",
